<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-5">Faith services</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Prayer area<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">On-site chapel<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent9a2127378d8343ecae73b40921d9d752">
</div>
<p>We have a chaplaincy department which can meet our patients' religious needs. The team consists of Church of England, Free Church, Roman Catholic and Muslim chaplains. If you would like to request a visit from one of the chaplains or any other religious leader, please ask a member of staff.  The Prayer Centre is situated by the Main Reception and opposite the restaurant. Times of all services are shown on the ward notice boards.</p>
</div>
